    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it does show signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits some fading and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it may require some routine maintenance in the near future, such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It is a solid, functional choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
