    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s running smooth and looking sharp. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
