    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, featuring crisp induction notes from the individual throttle bodies. Crucially, the 'Big Three' have been addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system overhauled, and rod bearings replaced with treated shells. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, offering the communicative steering feel these chassis are known for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical tolerances and drivetrain integrity make this a turn-key enthusiast's tool.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
